{"tid":874495,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"的士司機遭警箍頸後亡　陪審團3比2裁定不合法被殺","createTime":"2018-10-24T08:42:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-24T08:42:28.000Z","uid":1002,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"030f61fffda35eddffbcf29fae3f2c3beb3c1e2e","tid":874495,"uid":1002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T08:42:28.000Z","msg":"警方6年前拘捕一名的士司機時，疑使用過分武力制服及押上警車致司機頸椎移位，全身癱瘓臥牀近一個月後不治，死因庭的陪審團今日退庭商議約6小時後，以3比2裁定司機死於不合法被殺，即同意涉箍頸警員誤殺司機。<br />\n<br />\n案發於2012年11月11日晚上，事主陳輝旺（終年65歲）在西隧收費亭附近，因車資問題與日籍乘客爭執動武。警察接報到場，調查後因事主打乘客，以普通襲擊拘捕他。事主由數名警員合力帶上警車，其間不斷掙扎，警員林偉榮疑箍到事主頸部，事主最終送院治理。兩日後，院方發現事主頸椎移位，引致全身癱瘓，留院治療一個月後，於同年12月12日因支氣管肺炎死亡。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181024/s00001/1540369802237\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181024%2Fs00001%2F1540369802237&d=pHDFri3JC9cxyroEx5P5vL5jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=b1bea9c9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181024%2Fs00001%2F1540369802237&h=cec7e253\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181024/s00001/1540369802237</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://style.vjmedia.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/74206.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstyle.vjmedia.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F06%2F74206.jpg&h=103f1949&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}